<item>
            <title>[QPIDJMS-300] Possible thread leak on simultaneous local and remote connection close</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPIDJMS-300</link>
                <project id="12314524" key="QPIDJMS">Qpid JMS</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;During a simultaneous close of a connection on both the local and remote side there is a race that can lead to the completion executor used in the session being left in a running state which can hold other resources captive and prevent GC. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13087630">QPIDJMS-300</key>
            <summary>Possible thread leak on simultaneous local and remote connection close</summary>
